args: Ninjas live in the shadows\nand protect their masters.
They possess unique knowledge and skills,\nmost of which are shrouded in mystery!
Nothing out of the ordinary tonight.\n...Hmm? Who goes there?!
It is Aoi. ...But what is that scroll\nshe holds in her hands?
You must give the password.\n＂The firefly that does not cry...＂
＂...is racked by the pain of love.＂
At last, the scroll filled with confidential\nninja attraction techniques!
That's right! If you use these babies,\nyou can make anyone fall for you.
This should prove most enlightening.\nYou have my thanks.
Laa de laa ♪ Dum de dooo ♪\nCome get grubbies in your tummies ♪
I saw you hand over that scroll earlier.
The whole exchange looked very sinister.\nWhat exactly was written upon—
Hey, that reminds me! You ALSO have\na ninja pigeon friend, right?
Yes, but that is hardly the—
Here, take some of this! It's a special\nblend of seeds and grains I mixed myself.
Er, yes. Thank you. Now let us return\nto the matter of the scro—
Ooo! We never had a chance to talk\nabout our hometowns, did we?
Back in my home, it was traditional to\nspend a whole month training in the\nforest. What about you?
We were sent to an uninhabited island\nand forced to subsist on wild grasses.
Ha ha! Wild grass is the WORST, right?\nNinjas do love their survival training!
So it seems. Getting back to that scro—
Oh, Jurota! Do you like oatmeal?\nBecause I looove—
We may originate from different villages,\nbut we are fellow ninjas who serve the\nsame master.
I want to believe you would never bring\ndangerous ninja knowledge to this castle.
And so, I ask you again:\nWhat was written on that scroll?
Aooooi! I have a question about that\nNinja Charm Techniques: Volume 15\nscroll that I borrowed...
Oh my gosh, her timing is TERRIBLE.
Ah, there you are, Aoi. You may take this\nback now. It was quite a fascinating read!
The ＂Popular Ninja Make-Up Techniques＂\nand ＂Sneak Up on His Heart!＂ sections\nwere especially interesting.

I was also intrigued by the section where
they asked 100 female ninjas how to tell
what the object of your affection is
thinking about you.

Er, is something wrong? There isn't anyone
listening in on us, is there? Because I
would be very embarrassed if this were
to get out. ...VERY. ...EMBARRASSED.
Well, I will take my leave of you now.\nDo let me know when a new volume\ncomes out, all right?
It's just something used by female ninjas\nto help people fall in looooo... Umm...
It is clearly a text on ninja methods of\nwinning parties over during negotiation.\nLikely in the political arena.
Um...yeeees! That's abso-LUTELY\nwhat it is! Elisanne is very interested\nin...political...arenas.
Then you have my sincerest apologies\nfor my misunderstanding the issue.
Incidentally, for future reference,\nI would very much like to read it myse—
